Security problem is usually to do with dynamic creation of web contents&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://img.picui.cn/free/2024/10/30/672216b529859.png&#34; alt=&#34;img&#34;&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
